Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You pathetic, little maggots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You would knowingly\Nattack the invincible fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of pirates commanded by Captain\NUsopp of the Going Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Attack them!\NShow no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Geez. I really\Nexpected you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a little bit\Nmore lively than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] I'm finished!\N--[USOPP yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHeh, heh. Look! Our pirate mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Ussop's joined\Nwe got four people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that's almost a whole crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time\Nwe got our own flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NUh... Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really\Ngonna be our mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHeh. Whadya think? Nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mark should be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It should strike fear\Ninto our enemy's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If our enemies were\Nterrified infants,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then this would be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys really should've\Ntold me about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you didn't know\Nthis about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you can draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHeh. When it comes to painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a league of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been drawing graffiti\Nfor 50 years straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhoa! Fifty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That would mean\Nhe's an old man by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Which would give him\Nfive or six grandchildren,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't see 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] That is so cool!\N--Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! A priceless\Nwork of pirate art!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks a lot like you\Non that flag. Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how do you\Nlike this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That's actually\Npretty good, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Keep it! That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've finally settled on it.\NThis is gonna be our mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Usopp! Draw one\Non the sail, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NRight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOkay! It's all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the Going Merry\Nhas everything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,she could possibly need!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're the Weird Creature!\NGaimon and His Strange Friends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm pooped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Are we going the right\Nway? Seems kinda dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat's the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. There's no\Ndoubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do ya' see out\Nthere? Is it something cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Treasure Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the Treasure Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I've heard of that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm not surprised,\Nthis place is famous
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the world over. And so are\Nthe crazy stories about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What crazy stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend has it that\Nwhoever's dumb enough
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to sail close to the island\Nincurs a god's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know that all those\Nstories were true, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a god's wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that sounds pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! We're not gonna--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NLet's go to Treasure Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThis is gonna be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP whimpers, yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. This place is creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that somewhere\Non this island rests
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,an unimaginable fortune\Njust waiting to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, many pirates have\Nlanded here in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but they all fled\Nin absolute terror
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,before they ever got\Na chance to look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Absolute terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I'd be afraid, too.\NThey say one pirates' face
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly turned\Ninto a boar's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And another pirates'\Nmustache stretched out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,like a couple of snakes\Nand strangled him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] But, that's\Nnot true... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. I'm sure that\Nsome of those stories
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,are a bit of an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Don't talk anymore,\Nyou're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawns] I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nap time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[snores]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] How can he possibly\Nsleep in such a creepy place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] He's either dumb,\Nor he's got nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[SNAKE BUNNY screeches]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?!\NAre we in danger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was just making up a\Nlittle dance to liven things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP sings]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Come on,\Nstop that Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, USOPP scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ROOSTER DOG crows]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[PANDA BAT wails]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NLeave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who's there?!\N--[STRANGE VOICE] Leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys? Where's that\Nvoice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NI am the vengeful island god!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave at once if\Nyou value your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Island god?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE] Wait.\NYou guys are pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NAh... I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a god need to\Nask something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE ]\NI dunno. I-I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,take one more step\Ninto the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The instant you do, you\Nwill instantly receive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,my divine punishment\Nand meet your doom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,which is my punishment.\NWait, uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. That made\Nno sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What's his\Ndeal, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE] What did\Nyou say, straw hat boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ANIMALS roar]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWhat are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NThey used to be humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They came looking for treasure,\Nbut all they found was my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. You transformed them?!\NThen you are a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NLook at all these weird things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. So, is this a pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be a lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIG LION roars]\N--[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE] You stretchy\Nfreak of nature! What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I ate a Devil Fruit.\NSo now I'm a rubber person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NYeah right. A Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard those same\Nstupid stories
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,back when I was a pirate, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when you were a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE] I mean, uh...\NNo! I wasn't reminiscing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,about the old days!\NEnough of that kinda talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hear about\Nthe old days! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts? You're the\None who brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You faker! You sound too\Ndumb to be a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE] Shut up!\NIf you won't leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then prepare for my\Ndivine judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO snores]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really pushing\Nyour luck... "god".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NHow are you not dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] There you are.\N--[STRANGE VOICE] Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NI said don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, USOPP scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NNo! That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey "island god".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even mortals know bullets\Ncan't hurt a rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not, but I\Nstill hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE]\NYou're some kind of monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look. Found his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, USOPP]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NCould it be the island god?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, NAMI gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand me up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NIt's a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Awesome! He's like\Na talking scrub brush!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? You're not\Neven a minor deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more like a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Stand me up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NRelax. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'll let you off\Nwith a warning this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[STRANGE VOICE grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--[screaming]\N--[LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, USOPP]\NLuffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, USOPP gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There. You're all set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] You're a pretty\Npopular guy, Mr. Island God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So lemme get this straight,\Nthese crazy animals
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,helped you scare\Noff the pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,who came to this place\Nlooking for treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI've never seen a person
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,stuffed inside a\Ntreasure chest before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real life\N"jack in the box".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ironically I am in fact\Nin a box, and my name is--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a person! Not a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been stranded,\Nalone, on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and stuck in this contemptible\Nbox for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been all alone on this\Nisland for 20 years? Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just take a look at me.\NI got a beard like a wild man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And in all that time,\Nyou're the first people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've had a real\Nconversation with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you understand\Nhow painful that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh... here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all\Nover for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] How could you\Nhave slept through
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that's\Njust happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He finally sees him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out!\NHe's in a treasure chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a "jack in the\Nbox". But real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ironically I am in\Nfact in a box and my name is--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already been\Nthrough all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NZoro! Gimme a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww! What are you doing?!\NStop it would you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pulling my\Nhead off! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm afraid you're stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON]\NDon't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been stuck inside\Nthis blasted treasure chest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for so many years now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's slowly become\Na part of my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to break it,\Nyou'll break my body, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strange little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] All right guys enough\Nabout me, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not like any of\Nthose other pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who've come around here,\Nthat's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King\Nof the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] You're what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get the One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'm gonna\Nbe King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The One Piece?!\NDon't tell me you idiots
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,are actually planning to\Nsail on the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Yup! We got\Na chart right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line's a graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I once saw a group of pirates\Nwho had managed to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,from that horrible place,\Nand I'll never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an awful sight. They\Nwere just the hollow shells
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of the men that they used\Nto be. There's no telling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what horrors they witnessed\Nin that ghastly place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one among them\Neven tried to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen to me well\Nyoung pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors of the One Piece\Nspawn more rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been only 20 odd\Nyears since the start
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Great Pirate Era, and\Nthe One Piece is already
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a dream within a dream\Nbeyond a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which one of these\Nis the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno. Figured you could\Ntell me, Mr. scrub brush guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I never learned\Nhow to read a sea chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I never did, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NIgnorance is bliss, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, even if we do some how\Nmake it to the Grand Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the best idea would be\Nto get as much treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,as we can and then escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead and do that,\NI'm gonna find the One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you get all that\Nconfidence of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI'll get it! You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exactly like me.\NYou even look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We could be twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say\Nhe looks like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man. I understand about\Nthe pursuit of your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a younger man,\Nwe used to feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We were willing to put\Nour lives on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to search for treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that single-minded zeal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that changed the course\Nof my life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Slow down.\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened 20 years ago...\NI was a much younger man then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My fellow pirates and\NI landed on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with a single purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To find the treasure\Nthat was said to rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN] Two-hundred men have\Nsearched for an entire month,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing has been found!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The only treasure chest\Nwe've uncovered is empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pack up men! We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES grumble]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A] What are you looking\Nat Gaimon? It's time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON]\NDid anyone look way up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that the captain stayed\Ndown here the whole month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON] I'd better go\Nahead and double check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON]\NI couldn't believe my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I found it.\NGuys, it's up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guy--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON] That's when I\Ngot stuck in this chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON] When I came to, my crew\Nwas already far out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Yes.\NI believe this means
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that the entire fortune\Nbelongs to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't climb up like this! I\Ncan't get out! I can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come back!\NCome back, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And after all this time, the\Nfortune I found but only saw
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for an instant has never strayed\Nfar from my lonely old mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates have come here countless\Ntimes to search for my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But fortunately my friends\Nhere, help me scare them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I've kept my\Ntreasure safe and sound
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for the past twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No question.\NIt's yours all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think we\Ncan help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaimon, why don't we get the\Ntreasure down for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Wait, Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you a thief that\Nonly steals from pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHow rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a thief, but I\Nhave a conscience!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the place.\NIt's all up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to it Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! The chests! You see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I found 'em! Six\Ntreasure chests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Good work! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's mine! I got my\Ntreasure! C'mon toss it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it! Go ahead\Nand toss it down boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna.\NSucks for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of crap is that,\NLuffy? Give the man his gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass! That treasure\Nbelongs to Gaimon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know it!\NToss it all down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not joking\Naround, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON]\NIt doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NIt's not all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaimon. You've been\Nguarding that treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with your heart and soul\Nfor the past 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON]\NStraw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a great guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. What do you\Nmean he's great?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I always had an inkling that...\Nthis might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried not to think\Nabout it. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[cries] They're empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYep. Every last one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How sad. The treasure he\Nguarded for 20 long years
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,was just a bunch of empty boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON]\NIt happens all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with treasures that have\Nmaps leading to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You set out on a\Nquest to find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but some one else\Ngot to it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of\Nrisk you have to take
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're a treasure\Nhunting pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can waste a whole\Nlifetime searching
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and never once touch treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty of pirates lived\Nlike that. Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Try not to\Nbe too upset, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing we came\Nalong after twenty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty years later, and\Nyou might've been dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy...\N--Is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this treasure hunt's\Na bust, you're gonna need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,something else to\Nfill your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join up with us\Nand search for the One Piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?\NYou're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I know how\NI must look to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people wouldn't even\Nspeak to me, but you were kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so many years since\NI've had a friend! [cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Are you sure you wanna\Nstay on the island, Gaimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure. There's something\Nhere far more valuable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,than treasure that\NI feel I must protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Worth more than gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For the past 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,these guys have stood by my\Nside through thick and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[GAIMON] Now that I know\Nthere's no treasure here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow finally feel free.\NWithout that heavy burden
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can concentrate on the things\Nthat really matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides,\Nafter all these years
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown fond of\Nthis little box.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad! You're a neat guy.\NPretty cool for a scrub brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The weird creatures here\Nare your true friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Yep! And he's\Nthe weirdest of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, USOPP, ZORO laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya! Take care okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Gaimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever give up on making\Nall your dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If the legendary One\NPiece exists out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's yours.\NI hope it finds you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you have\Nit, buy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.54,0:24:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.37,0:24:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you start\Nusing the Three-Sword Style?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.67,0:24:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NOh, well--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NStop being stupid, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.08,0:24:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro would never tell\Nanyone about himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.21,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NActually...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] One sword is different\Nfrom the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.04,0:24:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHe just couldn't get a full set!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.58,0:24:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] It's just an\Nordinary old sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.08,0:24:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.25,0:24:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NShut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.92,0:24:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.67,0:24:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Three-Sword Style's past!\NZoro and Kuina's vow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.37,0:24:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King\Nof the Pirates!

